# Deploy allowlist (gitignore syntax): `/*` ignores everything at the repo root, then each `!` re-includes one entry the app loads at runtime.
# scrollview-web is here only because a lazy dynamic import reaches it during OCR.
# Adding a new top-level runtime dependency means adding a matching `!` line here.
/*
!/index.html
!/js/
!/scribe-ui/
!/scribe.js
!/fonts/
!/tess/
!/lib/
!/scrollview-web/
